截止2015年11月，本场飓风仍然保持着多项纪录：风速方面是除了2015年的颶風帕特里夏外；所有已知登陆过的东太平洋飓风中最高的<ref name="Kenna 02 TCR">{{cite report |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2002kenna.shtml |title=Hurricane Kenna 2002 |author1=Franklin, James L |type=Tropical Cyclone Report |accessdate=2013-11-22 |date=2002-12-26 |publisher=United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service |archivedate=2013-10-19 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019193942/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/2002kenna.shtml }}</ref>。而在墨西哥登陆过的一共六个[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]达到五级的热带气旋中<ref name="Jauregui" /><ref name="NHC Dean">{{cite web |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL042007_Dean.pdf |page=8 |title=Tropical Cyclone Report Hurricane Dean |author=James Franklin |date=2008-01-31 |format=PDF |accessdate=2013-12-10 |publisher=National Hurricane Center |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012024447/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL042007_Dean.pdf |archivedate=2013-10-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，只有这飓风和帕特里夏是在该国太平洋海岸登陆的<ref name="Jauregui" />。另外四个分别是{{link-en|飓风珍妮特|Hurricane Janet}}、[[飓风安妮塔|飓风安妮塔]]，[[颶風吉爾伯特|颶風吉爾伯特]]<ref name="Jauregui" />和[[飓风迪安|飓风迪安]]，均为[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]<ref name="NHC Dean"/>。同时，本场飓风和帕特里夏也是僅有兩個有实际登陆的五级太平洋飓风<ref name="best track" /><ref name="revised best track" /><ref name="Kenna 02 TCR" />。此外，飓风迟至10月27日达到五级强度，这也是任何一个太平洋飓风季中有气旋达到该强度的最晚日期<ref name="best track" />。并且还是有记载的第一个在东太平洋（西经140度到[[北美洲|北美洲]]之间）形成并达到五级强度的太平洋飓风，之前唯一一个达到这一强度的太平洋飓风是在中太平洋（西经140度到[[国际日期变更线|国际日期变更线]]）形成的<ref name="best track" />。

这个气旋还是造成人员死亡最多的东太平洋飓风，共计造成的死亡人数也比其他任何一个已知的太平洋飓风要高<ref name="National Geographic" /><ref name="Jauregui" /><ref name="Whipple">{{cite book |title=Storm |url=https://archive.org/details/stormwhip00whip |author=Addison Whipple |publisher=Time Life Books |page=[https://archive.org/details/stormwhip00whip/page/103 103] |year=1982 |isbn=978-0-8094-4312-3}}</ref>。包括1982年的飓风保罗<ref name="paul1" /><ref name="paul2" /><ref name="paul3" /><ref name="paul4" /><ref name="24KFH" /><ref name="Gunther et al. 1982">{{cite web|url=http://ams.allenpress.com/archive/1520-0493/111/5/pdf/i1520-0493-111-5-1080.pdf |publisher=American Meteorological Society |work=Monthly Weather Review |author=E.B. Gunther, R.L. Cross, & R.A. Wagoner |accessdate=2007-12-13 |title=Eastern North Pacific Tropical Cyclones of 1982 |pages=1080, 1097–8 |format=PDF |archivedate=2011-05-15 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110515040303/http://ams.allenpress.com/archive/1520-0493/111/5/pdf/i1520-0493-111-5-1080.pdf |date=1983年5月 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>和1976年的飓风丽莎<ref name="National Geographic" /><ref name="Gunther 1976">{{cite web |work=Monthly Weather Review |publisher=American Meteorological Society |page=508 |author=Emil B. Gunther |url=http://ams.allenpress.com/archive/1520-0493/105/4/pdf/i1520-0493-105-4-508.pdf |title=Eastern North Pacific Tropical Cyclones of 1976 |format=PDF |accessdate=2007-12-24 |archivedate=2011-06-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110612020459/http://ams.allenpress.com/archive/1520-0493/105/4/pdf/i1520-0493-105-4-508.pdf |date=1977年4月 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="Clifford">{{cite book |author=Mary E. Clifford |title=News Dictionary 1976 |url=https://archive.org/details/1976newsdictiona0000unse |publisher=Facts On File |year=1977 |isbn=978-0-87196-103-7}}</ref>。后两个是已知仅有的，另外两个造成上千人死亡的风暴<ref name="1976 SS">{{cite journal | last = Gunther | first = Emil B. | title = Eastern Pacific Tropical Cyclones of 1976 | volume = 105 | date = 1977-04-01 | journal = Monthly Weather Review | pages = 508-522 | url = http://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/pdf/10.1175/1520-0493%281977%29105%3C0508%3AEPTCO%3E2.0.CO%3B2 | accessdate = 2013-11-22 | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1977)105<0508:EPTCO>2.0.CO;2 | issue = 4 | bibcode = 1977MWRv..105..508G | archive-date = 2020-05-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200528143839/https://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/pdf/10.1175/1520-0493%281977%29105%3C0508%3AEPTCO%3E2.0.CO%3B2 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="MXGUTTAFSV" /><ref name="HLRM" />。
